[SN]TITLE[SN]
Music helps seven-year-old to speak

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Ruweyda is seven years old and has only recently said her first words at school.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
31 March 2017 Last updated at 09:10 BST
That's because she has a very strong type of anxiety called selective mutism.
But she's started taking a special music class which has helped her to speak at school.
Meet Ruweyda by watching our video.
